12 (g) [Proceeds] EXCEPT AS REQUIRED BY SUBSECTION (F)(14) OF THIS
13 SECTION, PROCEEDS received by the Fund from the sale of allowances under § 2–1002(g)
14 of the Environment Article shall be allocated as follows:
15 (1) at least [50%] 65% shall be credited to an energy assistance account to
